#

Vegetable Stir-Fry with Tofu

25 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyEasyOne-Pan

Description

A vibrant and healthy mix of fresh vegetables and protein-packed tofu stir-fried in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • mixed vegetables (bell peppers, broccoli, carrots): 4 cups
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • sesame oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (minced): 1 inch
  • green onions (sliced): 2
  • salt and pepper: to taste
